2011-12-07T19:58:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/viacom-sells-400-million-2-5-5-year-sr-unsecured-notes.html
The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:      Viacom
Manager(s):  Bank of America Merrill Lynch  Citigroup Global Markets Inc  Mizuho Securities USA Inc  RBS Securities Corp  SMBC Securities
Amount:      $400 million
Coupon:      2.5 percent
Maturity:    Dec. 15, 2016
Settlement:  Dec. 12, 2011
Spread:      175 basis points more than governments
 